OL,6,F"And let's be respectful of each other
OL,7,Fto have a debate about, 'what's the
OL,8,Fconstitutional future look like for us
OL,9,Fall?'
OL,11,F"And how do we find a way to do better
OL,12,Ffor both those of an Irish identity,
OL,13,Fthose of a British identity, who share
OL,14,Four island because it's our place,
OL,15,Fthat's our home.
OL,17,F"We have work to do better for us all."
