OL,6,FAsked about her comments, the DUP
OL,7,FEducation Minister Paul Givan told UTV
OL,8,Fhe was focused on his new role in the
OL,9,FExecutive.
OL,11,F"I want the Assembly and Executive
OL,12,Ffocused to be about delivering for all
OL,13,Fthe bread and butter issues," he said.
OL,15,F"I think the public expect the first
OL,16,Fminister and all of us to get on with
OL,17,Fthe job and not focus on a border poll
OL,18,Fand typically when it comes to key
OL,19,Fmoments after elections or the
OL,20,Fappointment of first ministers for
OL,21,FSinn Fein they go to border polling.
